IMPORTANT - Responsible use
------------------------------------------------------------------------
This software scores human job applicants using a large language model.
Automated assessment of candidates is a high-risk activity under several
regulatory frameworks (e.g. the EU AI Act, and US EEOC guidance). The
output is decision-support only and MUST be reviewed by a human. It must
not be used to automatically reject candidates. See the "Responsible &
ethical use" section of README.md before deploying.
